      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait what? why did you mention a goblin lol. anyway back to the sink: i think i've got the handle off now but i'm stuck on the stem part. it seems a bit stuck and i'm worried i'm gonna snap something if i pull too hard on it with the wrench. is there a trick to getting it loose?",
